6/12/2023 :
    installing and configuring softwares in ec2 server (ubuntu) --->
        1. install via tar/zip file using sudo wget <link> command
        2. once installed extract files 
        3. setup environment variable in /etc/profile.
        4. run source /etc/profile to load environment variables.
        
    configuring agent on Jenkins : -->
        1. setup credentials with key and username of your server.
        2. setup tools.
        3. now configure your node and add tools.

